RT|date=2020-03-20|website=vrtnws.be|language=nl|access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref>}}\n|}\n\n==Hostings==\n<!-- DO NOT add flagicons to the host city column.  This article is already about Belgium, so there is no need to highlight with {{flagicon}} that the city is in Belgium. This is in accordance with [[WP:ICONDECORATION]]. -->\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|- \n! Year\n! Location\n! Venue\n! Presenter\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1987}}\n| [[Brussels]]\n| [[Heysel Park|Centenary Palace]]\n| [[Viktor Lazlo]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards==\n===Barbara Dex Award===\n{{further|Barbara Dex Award}}\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n!Year\n!Performer\n!Host city\n!{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2000}}\n|[[Nathalie Sorce]]\n|{{flagicon|Sweden}} [[Stockholm]]\n|{{center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2015/07/09/poll-worst-dressed-barbara-dex-award-winner/|title=Poll: Who was the worst dressed Barbara Dex Award winner?|publisher=[[Wiwibloggs]]|date=9 July 2015|accessdate=8 December 2019|first=William Lee|last=Adams}}</ref>}}\n|}\n\n==Related involvement==\n===Commentators and spokespersons===\n{{more citations needed section|date=December 2019}}\nBelgium has two public broadcast stations [[Vlaamse Radio- en Televisieomroep|VRT]] (Dutch speaking region) & [[RTBF]] (French speaking region). Both broadcast the event and over the years VRT and RTBF commentary has been provided by several experienced radio and television presenters, including [[Nand Baert]], [[Jacques Mercier]], [[Luc Appermont]] and [[Paule Herreman]]. However, from the [[Eurovision Song Contest 1991|1991 Contest]], [[Andr\u00e9 Vermeulen]] has provided the Dutch language commentary every year, with the exception of the [[Eurovision Song Contest 1996|1996 Contest]]. Whilst [[Jean-Pierre Hautier]] has provided the French language commentary every year since the [[Eurovision Song Contest 1994|1994 Contest]] until the 2013 contest. In 1962, then BRT used the commentary from [[Nederlandse Omroep Stichting|NOS]] (The Netherlands broadcast), the reason for that was unknown.\n\nSince 1998 VRT has supplied a dual commentator to join [[Andr\u00e9 Vermeulen]], between 1999 and 2010 Dual commentary was provided by [[Bart Peeters]] and [[Anja Daems]]. Peeters provided the commentary during the years when VRT selected the entries whilst Daems commentated the years RTBF selected the entries. Since 2011 Sven Pichal has replaced Daems as commentator, whilst [[Peter Van de Veire]] has replaced Peeters. Since 2007 Jean-Louis Lahaye has joint [[Jean-Pierre Hautier]] as dual commentator for [[RTBF]]. After Hautier's death in 2012 Lahaye was joined by [[Maureen Louys]] in 2013.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Flemish commentator\n!French-speaking commentator\n!Spokesperson\n!class=\"unsortable\"|{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1956}}\n|[[Nand Baert]] ||rowspan=\"2\"|Janine Lambotte ||{{N/A|No spokesperson}} ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1957}}\n|rowspan=\"5\"|Nic Bal ||Bert Leysen ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1958}}\n|Arlette Vincent ||[[Paule Herreman]] ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1959}}\n|Paule Herreman ||Bert Leysen ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1960}}\n|Georges D\u00e9sir ||Arlette Vincent ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1961}}\n|Robert Beauvais ||Ward Bogaert ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1962}}\n|[[Willem Duys]] ||[[Nicole V\u00e9dr\u00e8s]] ||Arlette Vincent ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1963}}\n|Herman Verelst, Denise Maes ||Pierre Delhasse ||Ward Bogaert  ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1964}}\n|rowspan=\"6\" |Herman Verelst||rowspan=\"3\" |Paule Herreman||Andr\u00e9 Hagon ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1965}}\n|Ward Bogaert ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1966}}\n|Andr\u00e9 Hagon ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1967}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Janine Lambotte ||Ward Bogaert ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1968}}\n|Andr\u00e9 Hagon ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1969}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Paule Herreman ||Ward Bogaert ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1970}}\n|Jan Theys ||Andr\u00e9 Hagon ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1971}}\n|rowspan=\"4\"|Herman Verelst ||Janine Lambotte ||rowspan=\"3\" {{N/A|No spokesperson}} ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1972}}\n|Arlette Vincent ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1973}}\n|Paule Herreman ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1974}}\n|Georges D\u00e9sir ||Andr\u00e9 Hagon ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1975}}\n|Willem Duys ||Paule Herreman ||Ward Bogaert ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1976}}\n|rowspan=\"15\"|[[Luc Appermont]] ||Georges D\u00e9sir ||Andr\u00e9 Hagon ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1977}}\n|Patrick Duhamel ||An Ploegaerts ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1978}}\n|[[Claude Delacroix]] ||Andr\u00e9 Hagon ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1979}}\n|Paule Herreman ||An Ploegaerts ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1980}}\n|rowspan=\"7\"|[[Jacques Mercier]] ||Jacques Olivier ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1981}}\n|Walter De Meyere ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1982}}\n|Jacques Olivier ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1983}}\n|An Ploegaerts ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1984}}\n|Jacques Olivier ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1985}}\n|An Ploegaerts ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1986}}\n|Jacques Olivier ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1987}}\n|Claude Delacroix ||An Ploegaerts ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1988}}\n|Pierre Collard-Bovy  ||Jacques Olivier ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1989}}\n|Jacques Mercier ||An Ploegaerts ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1990}}\n|rowspan=\"4\"|Claude Delacroix ||Jacques Olivier ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1991}}\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[Andr\u00e9 Vermeulen]] ||An Ploegaerts ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1992}}\n|Jacques Olivier ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1993}}\n|An Ploegaerts ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1994}}\n|rowspan=\"2\" |[[Jean-Pierre Hautier]] ||{{N/A|Did not participate}} ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|1995}}\n|Marie-Fran\u00e7oise Renson \"Soda\" |