ad, including current team captain [[Zhu Ting (volleyball)|Zhu Ting]], former team captain [[Hui Ruoqi]], setter [[Ding Xia]], middle blockers [[Xu Yunli]], [[Yan Ni (volleyball)|Yan Ni]], [[Yuan Xinyue]], outside hitters [[Zhang Changning]], [[Liu Xiaotong|Liu XIao Tong,]] opposite spiker [[Gong Xiangyu]] and libero [[Lin Li (volleyball)|Lin Li]], were cast to play themselves in the film. The current national team setter [[Yao Di (volleyball)|Yao Di]] was cast to play setter [[Wei Qiuyue]], who was pregnant at the time of filming. \n\n==See also==\n*[[China women's national under-23 volleyball team]]\n*[[China women's national under-20 volleyball team]]\n*[[China women's national under-18 volleyball team]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20140908181619/http://www.volleyball.org.cn/ Official website]\n*[http://www.fivb.org/EN/FIVB/Federation.asp?NF=CHN FIVB profile]\n\n{{National sports teams of China}}\n{{Women's AVC teams}}\n{{Summer Olympics Women's Volleyball tournament winners}}\n{{Women's Volleyball World Championship winners}}\n{{Women's Volleyball World Cup winners}}\n{{FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix winners}}\n{{Asian Games volleyball women's tournament winners}}\n{{Asian Women's Volleyball Championship winners}}\n{{Asian Women's Volleyball Cup winners}}\n\n[[Category:China national volleyball team]]\n[[Category:Women's national sports teams of China|Volleyball]]\n[[Category:National women's volleyball teams]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox national volleyball team\n|name          = China\n|gender        = women\n|image         = Flag of the People's Republic of China.svg\n|federation    = [[Chinese Volleyball Association]] (CVA)\n|website       = [http://www.volleyball.org.cn/ www.volleyball.org.cn] {{in lang|zh}}\n|confederation = AVC\n|manager       = \n|coach         = [[Lang Ping]]\n|Olympic apps  = 9\n|Olympic first = 1984\n|Olympic best  = {{OG1}} ([[Volleyball at the 1984 Summer Olympics|1984]], [[Vo